      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Correspondence between experimental and simulation input parameters must be documented.",
      "rationale": "Not assessed at MRL 2. Nominal equivalency established through boundary condition matching documented in the test conditions factor. Formal equivalency analysis deferred to MRL 3 assessment if device risk level increases."
    }
